Fry @steel cut oats{1%cup} in @butter until all is absorberd.
Add @water{3%cups} and bring to boil. 
Lower heat and simmer for ~{30%minutes} with lid on. Stirring every 10 minutes
Add @milk{1%cup} and a small pinch of @salt 
Increase heat, and cook for ~{10%minutes} while stirring.
